

NAME
====

Joose.Manual.Delta - Important Changes in Joose

DESCRIPTION
===========

This documents any important or noteworthy changes in Joose, with a focus on backwards. This does duplicate data from the Changes file, but aims to provide more details and when possible workarounds.

Besides helping keep up with changes, you can also use this document for finding the lowest version of Joose that supported a given feature. 
If you encounter a problem and have a solution but don't see it documented here, or think we missed an important feature, please send us a patch.

